Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in central El Paso just off Interstate 10 and south of Bassett Place Mall, it offers a convenient commute from any part of town and easy access for companies with business in Cd. Juarez. The El Paso International Airport is 2.5 miles away. Ample amenities nearby include: restaurants, hotels, shopping, Medical Center of the Americas, with easy access to Interstate 10 and Highway 54.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Tri-State Plaza is a four-story Class A office building that is professionally managed & maintained by a dedicated on-site team to meet the needs of its tenants. There are several suites that are move-in ready ranging from a single office, up to Â± 3,950 SF. There is ï¬exibility to customize a ï¬oor plan to suit the requirements of any office tenant. Ownership is also willing to work with its tenants as their business grows, offering ï¬exibility to move into other suites within the building as needed.

The building offers 24/7 card access. In addition to round the clock access, tenants have the security that only those with access cards are able to enter the building after building hours. There is also ample parking all around the building, including covered parking.
